sentence: Which courses are offered this semester ?
sentence-with-vars: Which courses are offered this semester ?
sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 , SEMESTER AS SEMESTERalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER = "WN" AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SEMESTER AND SEMESTERalias0.YEAR = 2016 ;

SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 WHERE COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SEMESTER = 2070 AND COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID ;
